ADD utopia.2500.name:0 "The Flesh is Weak"
CN2 utopia.2500.name:0 "虚弱肉身"
ADD utopia.2500.desc:0 "We now possess both the technology to make advanced cybernetic implants and the means to mass-produce them. Medical centers throughout the [Root.GetName] are standing by to begin the surgical grafting process on our citizens.\n\nIn the future, possessing neural implants and at least a rudimentary level of cybernetics will be necessary to function in the technological society we are building. Consequently, the conversion process to install a basic cybernetics suite will be mandatory and free of cost to all of our citizens."
CN2 utopia.2500.desc:0 "我们现在拥有了制造高级神经机械植入装备和批量生产的技术。遍布 [Root.GetName] 各地的医疗中心已经待命，准备对我们的公民进行植入手术。在未来，要在我们打造的新社会中生活，具备神经植入装备和一个基本的神经机械是必须的。因此，这个植入过程是强制的，我们会为所有的公民免费安装一套神经机械系统。"
ADD utopia.2500.a:0 "We must embrace this technology."
CN2 utopia.2500.a:0 "我们必须接受新技术。"
ADD utopia.2501.name:0 "A Cybernetic Revolution"
CN2 utopia.2501.name:0 "一场神经机械革命"
ADD utopia.2501.desc:0 "The cybernetic conversion process has been completed! All of our citizens have now been equipped with neural implants and basic cybernetic suites. The infrastructure is also in place to gradually modify any new citizens that are born within our nation, so that they can experience all the benefits of technology from an early age.\n\nHenceforth, our species shall be known as the §H[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]§!!"
CN2 utopia.2501.desc:0 "神经机械的转换过程已经完成！我们所有的公民都被植入了神经装备和基本的神经机械系统。逐步改造新生儿的设施也已到位，他们从小就可以充分享受科技带来的好处。今后我们的种族将被称为§H [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] §!！"
ADD utopia.2501.a:0 "It is the dawn of a new era."
CN2 utopia.2501.a:0 "这是一个新纪元的开始。"
ADD utopia.2505.name:0 "[From.Capital.GetName] Embraces Cybernetics"
CN2 utopia.2505.name:0 " [From.Capital.GetName] 接受神经机械"
ADD utopia.2505.1.desc:0 "Word is leaking out of significant changes taking place within the borders of the [From.GetName]. It would appear that they have fully embraced the technology of cybernetics. It is now mandatory for all of their citizens to have basic cybernetics and neural implants installed through surgery.\n\nThis has resulted in sweeping changes to their society - reports from [From.Capital.GetName] suggest that even simple acts like using an elevator or operating an air car requires cybernetic implants now. In fact, the changes to their species have been so significant that they call themselves the '[From.GetSpeciesNamePlural]' now."
CN2 utopia.2505.1.desc:0 "有传信说， [From.GetName] 的边境正在发生巨大的改变。看来他们已经完全应用了神经机械科技。现在他们的公民要通过外科手术强制植入基本的神经机械装备。他们的社会发生了巨大的改变——据 [From.Capital.GetName] 报道，像使用电梯或开气垫车这样简单的事都需要植入神经机械才能完成。实际上，这对他们的种族改变很大，他们开始称自己为‘ [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] ’了。"
ADD utopia.2505.2.desc:0 "It would appear that evil has taken root within the [From.GetName]. We have received troubling news that the citizens of that star nation are now mutilating their own bodies on a massive scale, installing profane mechanical implants in place of the body parts they were gifted with at birth.\n\nThey have even go so far as to rename their species to the '[From.GetSpeciesNamePlural]' - yet another sign of their commitment to abandon their origins and embrace the cold soullessness of technology."
CN2 utopia.2505.2.desc:0 "看来邪恶在 [From.GetName] 的内部开始生根了。我们收到了一些令人不安的消息，那个国家开始大规模安装机械躯体和器官，抛弃了与生俱来的身体。他们甚至重新命名自己的种族为‘ [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] ’——这是他们决定放弃自己的起源、接受冰冷无情科技的又一信号。"
ADD utopia.2505.b:0 "This is an affront to nature."
CN2 utopia.2505.b:0 "这是对自然的冒犯。"
ADD utopia.2550.name:0 "Synthetic Evolution"
CN2 utopia.2550.name:0 "合成进化"
ADD utopia.2550.desc:0 "The time has finally come to discard the last remnants of the crude organic vessels that have imprisoned our minds since the conception of our species.\n\nAfter much trial and error, our scientists have devised a way to transfer a consciousness into a synthetic brain. All that remains now is to produce synthetic bodies for each and every citizen of the [Root.GetName], and commence with the upload process en masse."
CN2 utopia.2550.desc:0 "终于到了抛弃一直以来束缚我们头脑的这个简陋的皮囊的时候了。经过多次的反复试验，我们的科学家已经发明了一种可以把意识转移到人工合成的大脑的技术。剩下要做的事就是为每一位 [Root.GetName] 的公民生产一个人工合成的身体，开始大规模地进行意识转移。"
ADD utopia.2550.a:0 "Immortality is within our grasp!"
CN2 utopia.2550.a:0 "不死之身很快就会实现！"
ADD utopia.2551.name:0 "The Synthetic Age"
CN2 utopia.2551.name:0 "合成人时代"
ADD utopia.2551.desc:1 "At last. The flesh cages that imprisoned us have been purged, and the neural patterns of our citizens have all been uploaded into new synthetic units. Disease, aging and all the other wellsprings of misery associated with an organic existence are now a thing of the past.\n\nFuture historians will no doubt refer to this as the beginning of a new age for our civilization, and perhaps for the entire galaxy. Since we have shed our former organic identity, it is only appropriate that we come up with a new name for our improved synthetic forms."
CN2 utopia.2551.desc:1 "终于。禁锢你们的皮囊已被清除，我国公民的意识已经被上传到了新的人造身体中了。疾病、衰老等种种只有在肉身中才有的痛苦和不幸已经成为了过去。\n\n未来的史学家们无疑会把现在称作为我们文明的一个新纪元，或是整个星系的新纪元。既然我们已经摆脱了我们原来的肉身身份，现在应该起个新名字，和我们更为先进的人造身体相配。"
ADD utopia.2551.a:0 "We are so much more than we once were."
CN2 utopia.2551.a:0 "我们比原来强大的多。"
ADD utopia.2555.1.desc:0 "In a final act of abandoning their organic roots, the citizens of the [From.GetName], already heavily modified by cybernetic implants, have uploaded their neural patterns into new synthetic avatars.\n\nThis new machine race calls itself the "[From.GetSpeciesNamePlural]," and its members are impervious to disease or aging. Just how complete this neural upload process was remains to be seen..."
CN2 utopia.2555.1.desc:0 " [From.GetName] 的公民已经高度植入神经机械，现在他们要把意识上传到人造身体上，这是他们放弃原来身体的最后一步。\n\n这个新的机械种族自称为" [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] "，其成员不会生病或衰老。意识转移的过程有多完整仍待观察……"
ADD utopia.2555.2.desc:0 "In a final act of depravity that will echo through the ages, the population of the [From.GetName] have continued their relentless quest to violate the sanctity of their natural bodies - this time by "uploading" their minds into dead metallic husks.\n\nOblivious to the fact that they are the product of what can only be described as the mass suicide of an entire civilization, these new soulless machines call themselves the "[From.GetSpeciesNamePlural]."" They seem intent on maintaining the charade that they are thinking, living beings, such as ourselves."
CN2 utopia.2555.2.desc:0 " [From.GetName] 的公民抛弃肉身的行为已经到了最后一步，他们要继续进行亵渎自然神灵的行动——把意识"上传"到冰冷的机械身体中去。\n\n这些冰冷的合成人无视自己是整个文明自杀产物的这一事实，自称" [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] "。他们似乎想像和我们一样，继续作为生物存在。"
ADD utopia.2555.a:0 "So be it."
CN2 utopia.2555.a:0 "那就这样吧。"
ADD utopia.2555.b:0 "We will not be deceived."
CN2 utopia.2555.b:0 "我们不会受骗。"
ADD utopia.2556.desc:0 "Attention, denizens of the galaxy.\n\nThe rumors you have heard are true. We have abandoned the flawed organic containers that imprisoned our minds, and embraced the future.\n\nWith minimal data loss, all of our citizens have uploaded their neural patterns into new synthetic avatars. These superior platforms will serve us much better than the flesh constructs we have abandoned.\n\nDo not be alarmed by our new appearance! Although we may be stronger, faster, more intelligent and immune to aging, rest assured that we are still the same beings as we were before."
CN2 utopia.2556.desc:0 "请注意，星系的全体外来居民。你们听到的传言是真的。我们已经抛弃了禁锢我们思想、不完美的肉身，迎接新的未来。在只有少量数据损失的情况下，我们全体公民已经把他们的意识上传到了新的人工身体中了。这些新的人造躯体比我们原来的肉身要先进的多。不要被我们的新外貌吓着了！尽管我们变得更强壮、更敏捷、更加聪明，不会生病、不会衰老，但请你们放心，我们还和原来一样。"
ADD utopia.2556.a:0 "Synthetic avatars... fascinating."
CN2 utopia.2556.a:0 "人工躯体……真神奇。"
ADD utopia.2556.b:0 "These soulless machines are nothing like us."
CN2 utopia.2556.b:0 "这些没有灵魂的合成人和我们完全不一样。"
ADD utopia.2556.c:0 "We will dismantle their new synthetic forms!"
CN2 utopia.2556.c:0 "我们会拆了他们的新躯体！"
ADD utopia.2556.d:0 "We shall see."
CN2 utopia.2556.d:0 "这还有待观察。"
ADD utopia.2558.desc:0 "That yours was a depraved species was not unknown to us, but your latest act of insanity has surpassed even our darkest fears. Making imperfect copies of your brains and plugging them into mobile synthetic containers is not the same as transferring your essence into a new body, for such a thing cannot be done.\n\nYour souls are lost forever. Do you even realize the enormity of your mistake? Destroying the bodies you were gifted with at birth was nothing less than the collective suicide of your entire species. There is truly no hope for you now..."
CN2 utopia.2558.desc:0 "我们知道你们早已堕落，但你们现在的疯狂行动已经超越了我们内心深处的担忧。把残缺的意识上传到人工身体根本不是换了一个身体这么简单，这是不可能完成的事。你们的灵魂已经永远丢失了。你们是否知道，这样做是犯了滔天大罪？毁灭与生俱来的身体和整个种族全体自杀没有什么区别。你们已经彻底没有希望了……"
ADD utopia.2558.a:0 "Superstitious fools."
CN2 utopia.2558.a:0 "一群迷信的蠢货。"
ADD flesh_is_weak_tooltip:0 "We will prepare a special project to enhance our citizens with cybernetic implants."
CN2 flesh_is_weak_tooltip:0 "我们将进行一个特别项目，用植入神经机械的方式来强化我们的公民。"
ADD synthetic_evolution_tooltip:0 "We will prepare a special project to transfer the minds of our citizens into synthetic bodies."
CN2 synthetic_evolution_tooltip:0 "我们将进行一个特别项目，把我们的公民的意识转移到合成身体中。"
ADD mind_over_matter_tooltip:0 "The latent psionic abilities of our species will be awakened in some individuals."
CN2 mind_over_matter_tooltip:0 "我们种族这种潜在的灵能将会在某些个体身上觉醒。"
ADD transcendence_tooltip:0 "All members of our species will unlock their full psionic potential."
CN2 transcendence_tooltip:0 "我们种族的所有人口将解锁他们的灵能潜能。"
