ADD utopia.2700.name:0 "Engineered Evolution"
CN2 utopia.2700.name:0 "人工进化"
ADD utopia.2700.desc:0 "Sometimes evolution needs a nudge in the right direction. We now have the technology to genetically modify our bodies and minds to endure the trials of an ever-changing environment at an unprecedented rate."
CN2 utopia.2700.desc:0 "有时进化就是需要往正确的方向上推一把。我们现在有足够先进的技术，能够对我们的身体和思维进行基因层面的改造，以应对不断变化的环境带来的前所未有的挑战。"
ADD utopia.2703.name:0 "Evolutionary Mastery"
CN2 utopia.2703.name:0 "进化支配"
ADD utopia.2703.desc:0 "Gone are the days when the survival of our species was at the mercy of chance. When a [Root.GetSpeciesName]'s fate was decided on the whims of nature, in the genetic lottery.\n\nThe Engineers of our time work not in steel and concrete, but in the very building blocks of life itself. With advanced gene modification we will secure the future of our nation."
CN2 utopia.2703.desc:0 "我们终于不用再担心种族的生死存亡了。 [Root.GetSpeciesName] 人被大自然主宰，基因进化完全听天由命的日子终于结束了。\n\n我们这个时代的工程师不是面对钢骨水泥工作，而是每天跟基因序列打交道。掌握着先进的基因改进技术，我们就能保证民族的美好未来了。"
ADD utopia.2600.name:0 "Mind over Matter"
CN2 utopia.2600.name:0 "心灵控制物质"
ADD utopia.2600.desc:0 "Since the dawn of our civilization, tales have flourished of mighty sorcerers wielding powers that can only be described as supernatural in nature. These rare [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] could supposedly invade the minds of their fellows, lift heavy objects with merely a thought, or perform any number of other "magical" feats. Until recently, these stories were just that - stories.\n\nNow, however, our scientists have finally obtained conclusive evidence that proves the psionic potential inherent in certain [Root.GetSpeciesName] individuals. Although only a very small minority of our species as a whole seems to be gifted with psionic powers, their numbers relative to the total population have grown steadily over just the last few centuries.\n\nWhether this is due to some kind of sudden evolutionary growth-spurt or because something has triggered latent psionic abilities that were always present in our genetic code, scientists cannot say."
CN2 utopia.2600.desc:0 "自我们的文明诞生以来，就流传着各种各样关于巫术的传说，这些可怕的巫术拥有超越自然的力量。极少数 [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 可以入侵同类的思想，通过意念举起重物，或是能办到其它任何"神奇"的事。直到最近，这些传说也只是——传说而已。不过现在，我们的科学家已经最终获得了关键性的证据，能够证明灵能潜藏在某些 [Root.GetSpeciesName] 个体中。尽管只有极少数人拥有灵能，但在过去几个世纪中，他们的比例在不断增加。是因为某种进化突变，还是因为某种物质诱发了潜存在我们基因代码中的灵能，科学家们现在还不得而知。"
ADD utopia.2600.a:0 "A glimpse, perhaps, of the future that awaits us."
CN2 utopia.2600.a:0 "在我们面前的，也许是对未来的一瞥。"
ADD utopia.2602.name:0 "[From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] Display Psionic Potential"
CN2 utopia.2602.name:0 " [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 显现灵能"
ADD utopia.2602.1.desc:0 "Latent psionic powers have begun to manifest in certain individuals belonging to the [From.GetSpeciesName] species, according to leaked reports from authorities in the §Y[From.GetName]§!. This must be a fairly recent development, since we have no record of [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] ever displaying psionic abilities on file.\n\nAccording to the leaked reports, these powers are so far limited to a very small minority of the [From.GetSpeciesName] species as a whole. Scientists in the §Y[From.GetName]§! have offered no explanation."
CN2 utopia.2602.1.desc:0 "根据一些泄露自 [From.GetName] 权威人士的报告，潜在的灵能已经开始在一些 [From.GetSpeciesName] 个体身上显现。这肯定是最近才显现的，因为我们从来没有 [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 显现灵能的记载。根据这些被泄露的报告，只有极少数 [From.GetSpeciesName] 具有这种能力。 [From.GetName] 的科学家对此无法解释。"
ADD utopia.2602.2.desc:0 "$utopia.2602.1.desc$\n\nThe [From.GetSpeciesName] population within our borders have begun exhibiting similar changes as well, so whatever is happening to their species is not localized to any single region of space."
CN2 utopia.2602.2.desc:0 "$utopia.2602.1.desc$我们边境内 [From.GetSpeciesName] 的个体也出现了相似的改变，所以无论他们的种族发生了什么，并不只限于当地。"
ADD utopia.2602.a:0 "How peculiar."
CN2 utopia.2602.a:0 "真奇怪。"
ADD utopia.2602.b:0 "Psychic powers? What a crock!"
CN2 utopia.2602.b:0 "特异功能？真荒谬！"
ADD utopia.2602.c:0 "Their sorcery will not be enough to save them."
CN2 utopia.2602.c:0 "他们的巫术无法救他们。"
ADD utopia.2602.d:0 "Yes... yes, we can sense their psychic emanations."
CN2 utopia.2602.d:0 "是的……是的，我们能感觉到他们的精神力。"
ADD utopia.2605.name:0 "[psionic_leader.GetTitle] Revealed as Psychic"
CN2 utopia.2605.name:0 " [psionic_leader.GetTitle] 显示了特异功能"
ADD utopia.2605.desc:0 "While it is rare for psionic powers to manifest after adolescence, it is not unheard of. [psionic_leader.GetTitle] [psionic_leader.GetName] has recently been displaying abilities that were suspected to be psionic in nature. After undergoing a thorough ESP test, [psionic_leader.GetSheHe] has been identified as a class 4 psionic talent."
CN2 utopia.2605.desc:0 "尽管在成年后显现出特异功能很少见，但并不是没有。 [psionic_leader.GetTitle]  [psionic_leader.GetName] 最近显示出了据说是灵能的能力。在经过了全面的心灵测试后，其被认定具有4级灵能。"
ADD utopia.2605.a:0 "These new abilities will serve us well."
CN2 utopia.2605.a:0 "这些新能力会对我们很有用。"
ADD utopia.2652.name:0 "[From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] Awaken Psionic Abilities"
CN2 utopia.2652.name:0 " [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 唤醒了灵能"
ADD utopia.2652.desc:0 "All [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] throughout the galaxy have undergone a great change. Whereas before their latent psionic power had only blossomed in a small minority, the entire species has now unlocked its full psychic potential.\n\nAlthough these changes seem to have originated in the [From.GetName], they have now manifested in all members of their species regardless of where they reside. Aside from displaying an array of powerful psionic abilities, [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] have started to forgo verbal communication with each other in favor of telepathy."
CN2 utopia.2652.desc:0 "整个星系中所有的 [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 都经历了一次巨大的改变。尽管原来这种潜在的能力只存在极少数人身上，但现在整个种族都有了特异功能。尽管这些改变似乎都源自 [From.GetName] ，但不管在哪儿，他们种族的所有人口现在都具备了这种能力。除了显现出了一系列超强的灵能， [From.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 已经开始不用口头交流，而改用意念交流。"
ADD utopia.2652.b:0 "There has to be a scientific explanation for this."
CN2 utopia.2652.b:0 "这一切肯定可以用科学解释。"
ADD utopia.2652.c:0 "This is not good..."
CN2 utopia.2652.c:0 "这不太好……"
ADD utopia.2652.d:0 "We felt the great psionic disturbance of their Awakening."
CN2 utopia.2652.d:0 "我们感到了他们觉醒所带来的强大灵能。"
ADD utopia.2650.name:0 "The Great Awakening"
CN2 utopia.2650.name:0 "大觉醒"
ADD utopia.2650.desc:0 "The [Root.GetSpeciesName] species has experienced what can only be described as a Great Awakening. For a time now, we have been aware of the great psionic potential inherent in our species, but such powers have only manifested themselves in a small minority... until now.\n\nAlmost overnight, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] everywhere have unlocked their full psionic capacity. It is as if some sort of communal pool of [Root.GetSpeciesName] psychic energy finally reached a critical tipping point, collectively awakening the latent abilities of our brains.\n\nTelepathy has already replaced most verbal communication between [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural], and this is only one small example of the innumerable changes our society is faced with. We are now tied together in a way few of us could have ever imagined."
CN2 utopia.2650.desc:0 " [Root.GetSpeciesName] 种族经历了一场可以被称为大觉醒的事件。一直以来，我们都知道灵能潜藏在我们的种族中，但只有极少数个体拥有……直到现在。几乎一夜之间，各地的 [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 都解锁了他们全部的灵能。这就好像 [Root.GetSpeciesName] 的精神能源到达了某种极限点，让我们所有个体的大脑集体唤醒了潜藏的特异能力。心灵感应已经代替口头交流，成了 [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 的交流方式，而这只是我们社会所面临的诸多改变中极其微小的一个。我们现在以一种以往几乎无法想像的方式结合在一起。"
ADD utopia.2650.a:0 "The veil has been lifted."
CN2 utopia.2650.a:0 "面纱已被揭开。"
ADD utopia.2655.name:0 "The Shroud"
CN2 utopia.2655.name:0 "灵能界"
ADD utopia.2655.desc:0 "Like a muffled whisper in a dark room, the Shroud calls to us from within our minds. It is a primordial realm of pure psychic energy that came into being at the dawn of time. All creatures that have been gifted with psionic abilities tap into the Shroud in some way to draw power, even if only subconsciously.\n\nSince our transcendence, we have begun to see the Shroud with greater clarity. There are patterns where once even our strongest telepaths could see only a formless mass of swirling energy. There are... other things, as well. Spirits of a sort, that gaze back on us from the other side. Sometimes with curiousity, sometimes with kindness... and sometimes with malice.\n\nWe are still in the process of learning the extent of our new powers, but it may be possible for us to commune with these spirits. It will require the combined efforts of our most powerful telepaths."
CN2 utopia.2655.desc:0 "就像黑暗房间中的低语，灵能界在我们的脑海深处向我们呼唤。这是一种原始的精神能源区域，在远古时代就存在。所有拥有这种灵能的个体都在一定程度上使用了精神能源区域的能源，即使是在无意识的情况下。自从我们放弃肉身后，我们开始能更加清楚地看到灵能界了。我们看到了一些图案，在过去，即使有最强的念力，看到的也只是一种无形、旋转的能源。现在我们还看到了……还看到了其它的东西。是某种灵魂，从另一面看着我们。有时带着好奇，有时带着仁慈……有时带着恶意。我们仍然在摸索我们新力能有多么强大，但我们也许可以用它来和这些灵魂交流。这需要把我们最强的念力集中起来。"
ADD utopia.2655.a:0 "We must explore the Shroud."
CN2 utopia.2655.a:0 "我们必须探索灵能界。"
ADD BREACHING_SHROUD_PROJECT:0 "Breaching the Shroud"
CN2 BREACHING_SHROUD_PROJECT:0 "突破灵能界"
ADD BREACHING_SHROUD_PROJECT_DESC:0 "If we are to communicate with the denizens of the psychic realm known as the Shroud, we will have to unleash an incredible amount of psionic energy. Preparations have been made for a huge séance involving our most powerful psychics in the newly established Conclave of Telepaths on [Root.Capital.GetName]."
CN2 BREACHING_SHROUD_PROJECT_DESC:0 "如果我们要和这些被称为灵能界的外来居民交流，我们必须爆发出非常大的灵能能源。我们已经准备好和这些灵魂进行一次交流，对话者来自 [Root.Capital.GetName] 刚刚成立的通灵会，他们是我们当中念力最强的。"
ADD utopia.2656.name:0 "The Séance"
CN2 utopia.2656.name:0 "通灵会"
ADD utopia.2656.desc:0 "After days of being locked in an hypnotic trance, our psychics in the Conclave of Telepaths have finally managed to open a brief gateway into the Shroud.\n\nNow that we have established an initial psionic link, we will be able to access the Shroud through the §HContacts§! menu in the future. To make any kind of meaningful forays into this realm and meet the beings who dwell there, we will likely have to make use of special psionic emitters to extend our psychic reach. This will consume a tremendous amount of energy."
CN2 utopia.2656.desc:0 "在昏迷了几天后，我们的对话者终于设法和灵能界建立了一个短暂的交流通道。既然我们已经建立了第一个灵能通道，那么我们就可以在未来通过§H联络§!菜单和灵能界交流。为了让这次与那里居民的会面交流更有意义，我们可能还需要使用特殊的灵能发射器去增加我们的灵力范围。这会消耗大量的能源。"
ADD utopia.2656.a:0 "Time to reach in and see what we find."
CN2 utopia.2656.a:0 "是时候看看我们找到了什么东西了。"
ADD utopia.3020.desc:0 "The powerful energies of the Shroud have been successfully channeled into a psionic Avatar under our control!\n\nAfter translating into our universe, the newborn Avatar has coalesced into a spacefaring entity in orbit over [Root.Capital.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.3020.desc:0 "灵能界强大的能源已经被成功地传输到了一个由我们控制的灵能化身！在转换到我们的世界后，这个新生的化身合成了一个飞行物，围绕 [Root.Capital.GetName] 飞行。"
ADD utopia.3021.desc:0 "The powerful energies of the Shroud have been successfully channeled into a psionic Avatar under our control!\n\nAfter translating into our universe, the newborn Avatar has coalesced into a colossal warrior on the surface of [Root.Capital.GetName]."
CN2 utopia.3021.desc:0 "灵能界强大的能源已经被成功地传输到了一个由我们控制的灵能化身！在转换到我们的世界后，这个新生的化身在 [Root.Capital.GetName] 的表面合成了一个巨大的武士。"
ADD utopia.3022.desc:0 "The psionic power required to summon an Avatar and bring it into our universe is simply beyond our current ability to channel. The psychic energies of the Shroud fizzle with agitation as our attempt fails."
CN2 utopia.3022.desc:0 "召唤灵能化身所需动用的灵能完全超乎了我们的掌控。我们的尝试最终以来自灵能界的灵能在激烈晃动中发出嘶嘶声而失败告终。"
ADD utopia.3023.desc:0 "The attempt to summon a psionic Avatar was only partially successful. Although the creature assumed its correct form and translated into our universe, our telepaths failed to bring it under our control!\n\nWe are now faced with an aggressive psionic entity that will destroy everything in its path!"
CN2 utopia.3023.desc:0 "召唤灵能化身的尝试只能算是成功了一半。虽然对方最终成功以物理形态降临了我们的世界，但是我们的通灵者却无法掌控对方！ \n\n我们召唤出来了一个六亲不认、极具侵略性的灵能怪物！"
ADD utopia.3024.name:0 "Shroud Incursion"
CN2 utopia.3024.name:0 "灵能界入侵"
ADD utopia.3024.desc:0 "A creature of the Shroud has pierced the fabric of space and materialized in the [shroud_spawn_system.GetName] system! This vengeful Avatar has amassed a tremendous amount of psionic energy, and is using it to lash out at anything and anyone unfortunate enough to get in its path."
CN2 utopia.3024.desc:0 "一只来自灵能界的生物穿越了空间构造降临在 [shroud_spawn_system.GetName] 星系中！这个暴戾的灵能化身积聚了大量的灵能能源，一路神挡杀神佛挡杀佛，把所有阻挡他步伐的人畜虾蟹都砸得灰飞烟灭。"
ADD utopia.3024.a:0 "It must be stopped!"
CN2 utopia.3024.a:0 "必须阻止它！"
ADD utopia.3026.name:0 "Shroud Avatar Banished"
CN2 utopia.3026.name:0 "灵能化身被驱逐"
ADD utopia.3026.desc:0 "The continual atrophy of existing in normal space has weakened the Avatar in the [shroud_spawn_system.GetName] system to the point where it can no longer maintain its tangible form. It has been banished back into the Shroud."
CN2 utopia.3026.desc:0 "长时间逗留在正常空间导致肆虐 [shroud_spawn_system.GetName] 星系的此灵能化身已经衰退到再也无法维持其实体形态了。该化身已被驱逐回灵能界。"
ADD utopia.3026.a:0 "Good riddance."
CN2 utopia.3026.a:0 "总算甩掉麻烦了。"
