ADD utopia.3000.name:0 "The Shroud"
CN2 utopia.3000.name:0 "灵能界"
ADD utopia.3000.a:0 "Reach into the Shroud."
CN2 utopia.3000.a:0 "进入灵能界。进入灵能界。"
ADD utopia.3000.intro.desc:0 "The Shroud. It is unbelievably strange and unsettling, but also... immediately familiar. Anyone with psionic powers will have seen this place in their dreams, though they likely did not know it at the time.\n\nWe linger now at the precipice of this realm, not far from the empty void of the Inbetween that serves as the boundary between here and normal space - or what we would call the real world.\n\nTo venture deeper into the Shroud will require great effort on the part of our telepaths, as well as a large amount of energy. We must not dally... even now, we are being watched."
CN2 utopia.3000.intro.desc:0 "灵能界。一个多么难以置信的神秘而又易变的地方，同时也那么的……让人立即能够熟悉起来。所有有灵能能力的人都在他的梦里见过这个地方，即使他们当时并没有认出来这里是哪儿。我们现在正在这个领域的绝壁处四处徘徊，这里离开正常空间跟这个领域之间的虚空处没多远。\n\n向灵能界更深处探索需要我们的通灵者出力的同时，也需要动用大量的能源。我们必须要抓紧时间……即使是现在，我们正被监视着。"
ADD utopia.3000.1.desc:0 "The Shroud is quiet today."
CN2 utopia.3000.1.desc:0 "今天灵能界真是安静。"
ADD utopia.3000.2.desc:0 "Something is watching us."
CN2 utopia.3000.2.desc:0 "有东西在注视着我们。"
ADD utopia.3000.3.desc:0 "It all looks so different on this side."
CN2 utopia.3000.3.desc:0 "从这边看事物一切都是如此的不同。"
ADD utopia.3000.4.desc:0 "They should have sent a poet..."
CN2 utopia.3000.4.desc:0 "可惜队伍中没有诗人……"
ADD utopia.3000.5.desc:0 "Something dark is coming."
CN2 utopia.3000.5.desc:0 "有个黑暗的东西在逼近我们。"
ADD utopia.3000.6.desc:0 "Are we still dreaming?"
CN2 utopia.3000.6.desc:0 "我们依旧在睡梦中么？"
ADD utopia.3000.7.desc:0 "We... we made it. We're inside!"
CN2 utopia.3000.7.desc:0 "我们……我们成功了。我们进去了！"
ADD utopia.3000.8.desc:0 "A... presence, of sorts, lingers nearby. It beckons us deeper into the Shroud..."
CN2 utopia.3000.8.desc:0 "一个未知的存在就在这里附近徘徊着。它招呼着我们往灵能界的深处前进……"
ADD utopia.3000.9.desc:0 "Do you hear the voices too?"
CN2 utopia.3000.9.desc:0 "你也听到那些声音了？"
ADD utopia.3000.10.desc:0 "The Shroud pulsates with power. It feels like... home."
CN2 utopia.3000.10.desc:0 "与灵能界一起悸动的能源。感觉就像是……家一样。"
ADD utopia.3000.11.desc:0 "Do you think that is air you're breathing now?"
CN2 utopia.3000.11.desc:0 "你觉得你们在呼吸的是空气么？"
ADD utopia.3000.12.desc:0 "We see, and yet we do not see. There is so much to learn about this place."
CN2 utopia.3000.12.desc:0 "我们也许知晓了一切，也许是一无所知。这里有太多知识等待我们去掌握。"
ADD utopia.3000.13.desc:0 "What senses do we lack that we cannot see and cannot hear another world all around us?"
CN2 utopia.3000.13.desc:0 "我们究竟是缺失了什么样的感官导致我们无法听亦或者看到我们身边的另一个世界？"
ADD utopia.3000.14.desc:0 "Take the greatest of care. Even a stray thought can be shaped into something tangible in this place... and, more often than not, turned against oneself."
CN2 utopia.3000.14.desc:0 "小心谨慎点。即使是一个迷离的想法也会在这里变成现实…然而最可怕的是，这个现实可能会成为自己的噩梦。"
ADD utopia.3000.15.desc:0 "We were never meant to be here."
CN2 utopia.3000.15.desc:0 "这里不该是我们踏足的地方。"
ADD utopia.3000.16.desc:0 "So... much... power..."
CN2 utopia.3000.16.desc:0 "如此……多的……能源……"
ADD utopia.3000.17.desc:0 "Must... focus..."
CN2 utopia.3000.17.desc:0 "必须……专注起来……"
ADD utopia.3000.18.desc:0 "Could this be where everything began?"
CN2 utopia.3000.18.desc:0 "这里难道就是万物之始？"
ADD utopia.3000.19.desc:0 "Horror... horror has a face."
CN2 utopia.3000.19.desc:0 "恐怖……恐怖有张面孔。"
ADD utopia.3010.desc:0 "The Conclave of Telepaths has not yet recovered from the strain of our previous visit to the Shroud. Without their combined psionic power, we can catch only brief glimpses of this fleeting realm - like the blurred edges of a memory lying just beyond reach.\n\nThere is nothing for us here. We will have to return later."
CN2 utopia.3010.desc:0 "通灵会还没有从上次探索灵能界的损伤中恢复过来。没有他们的全体灵能能力，我们也就只能对这个转瞬即逝的领域匆匆一瞥——就如一个模糊的记忆，虽近在眼前却永远触之不及。 \n\n这里暂时没有我们的事了。我们下次再回来吧。"
