ADD boon.psi.link:0 "The powerful energies of the Shroud have flooded into the communal psionic link that is shared between all [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]."
CN2 boon.psi.link:0 "灵能界的强大能源涌入了所有 [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 之间共享的公共灵能通道中。"
ADD boon.ship.link:0 "Our telepaths have managed to establish a temporary conduit between the Shroud and our starships."
CN2 boon.ship.link:0 "我们的通灵者成功在灵能界跟我们的星舰之间搭建了一条联系。"
ADD utopia.3030.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nA profound sense of calm is spreading throughout the [Root.GetName], and it seems to affect even those without psychic abilities."
CN2 utopia.3030.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$整个 [Root.GetName] 都在传播着一股宁静的感觉，哪怕是没有灵能能力的人也受到了影响。"
ADD utopia.3031.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nThe normal wear-and-tear that all starships suffer from has all but disappeared in our fleets. As a result, our upkeep costs have been significantly decreased."
CN2 utopia.3031.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$所有星舰上的正常磨损都彻底消失了。我们的维修费用也因此大幅降低了。"
ADD utopia.3032.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nA collective knowledge base that is shared telepathically between our scientists has been established, which will greatly increase the efficiency of their work."
CN2 utopia.3032.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$一个由科学家们以心灵感应方式共享的社会知识库已成功建立，此方法可以大幅增长科学家们的工作效率。"
ADD utopia.3033.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nThe crews of our warships can now augment the strength of our shield systems by using their psionic powers."
CN2 utopia.3033.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$我方战舰的船员可以使用他们的灵能来提高舰船护盾的威力了。"
ADD utopia.3034.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nUsing their psionic powers, our crewmembers are now able to augment the strength of our weapon systems."
CN2 utopia.3034.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$我方船员现在可以使用他们的灵能来提高舰船武器系统的威力了。"
ADD utopia.3035.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nUsing their psionic powers, our crewmembers are now able to increase the firing rate of our weapon systems."
CN2 utopia.3035.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$我方船员现在可以使用他们的灵能来提高舰船武器系统的射速了。"
ADD utopia.3036.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nA new sense of solidarity has appeared in the hearts and minds of our citizens, and they seem more willing to work together towards the mutual goals established by our government."
CN2 utopia.3036.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$我们的公民多了一股团结的责任感，大家变得更积极配合政府的工作来完成共同的目标。"
ADD utopia.3037.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nOur empaths are stronger than ever before, resulting in greater political influence."
CN2 utopia.3037.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$我们的感染力比以往更加强大了，我们的政治影响力也因此显著提高。"
ADD utopia.3038.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nWe have never felt a greater sense of unity."
CN2 utopia.3038.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$我们从未感到如现在一样的团结。"
ADD utopia.3039.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nUsing their psionic powers, our crewmembers are now able to directly affect the movement of our ships, increasing their evasiveness in the face of enemy fire."
CN2 utopia.3039.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$我方船员现在可以使用灵能来直接操纵舰船的移动，让我方舰船可以更加敏捷的躲避敌人的攻击。"
ADD utopia.3040.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nUsing their psionic powers, our crewmembers are now able to perform limited field repairs, mending hull fissures with their minds alone."
CN2 utopia.3040.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$我方船员现在可以使用灵能来展开有限的紧急维修，通过精神力来修复舰体的裂缝。"
ADD utopia.3041.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nOur telepaths have used this power to momentarily slow down the aging process for our most prominent leaders, adding decades to their natural lives. Alas, there was not enough psychic energy to bestow this effect upon the population at large."
CN2 utopia.3041.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$这种全新的力量瞬间大幅提升了包括非灵能者在内的所有公民的寿命！现在每个人都是健健康康的。"
ADD utopia.3042.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$\n\nUsing their psionic powers, our crewmembers are now able to augment the strength of the thrusters on their ships, resulting in greatly increased sub-light speed."
CN2 utopia.3042.desc:0 "$boon.ship.link$我方船员现在可以使用他们的灵能来提高舰船推进器的效率，导致其亚光速航行速度显著提升。"
ADD utopia.3043.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nThis has fortified the minds of our soldiers, who are now willing to brave any dangers on the battlefield. Their esprit de corps is without equal."
CN2 utopia.3043.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$战士们的心灵意志得到了强化，他们现在能够英勇面对战场上的任何危险。他们的团队精神也变得无与伦比。"
ADD utopia.3044.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$\n\nWe can now sense vessels as they move through space at a far greater distance than any conventional sensor array would be capable of."
CN2 utopia.3044.desc:0 "$boon.psi.link$我们现在可以感应到在遥远太空中航行的舰船，效果范围比传统的传感器阵列更加辽阔。"
ADD utopia.3045.1.desc:0 "The conduit that our telepaths were using to connect to the Shroud collapsed on itself as several energy layers of the psychic realm suddenly shifted without warning.\n\nWe are being summarily ejected back into normal space."
CN2 utopia.3045.1.desc:0 "我们的通灵者用于连接灵能界的联系因为灵能界的能源层毫无预兆地移动而崩溃了。\n\n我们暂时被强行驱逐回到正常空间。"
ADD utopia.3045.2.desc:0 "Our telepaths have been overwhelmed by the intense strain they were put under during our communion with the Shroud.\n\nThey can no longer maintain the link."
CN2 utopia.3045.2.desc:0 "我们的通灵者在跟灵能界沟通时被排山倒海的压力压倒了。他们已无法继续维持连接。"
ADD utopia.3045.3.desc:0 "Slowly at first, then faster and faster, our grasp on the Shroud begins to slip. Our telepaths cry out in anguish as they lose their foothold and we are ejected back into normal space."
CN2 utopia.3045.3.desc:0 "刚开始很慢，但随之逐渐加快，我们对灵能界的掌控开始变得越来越弱。我们的心灵感应者在彻底失去感应后不禁愤怒地叫骂出声。我们被驱回至正常空间。"
ADD curse.psi.link:0 "A powerful psychic backlash has bounced back through our conduit with the Shroud, and into the communal psionic link that is shared between all [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]."
CN2 curse.psi.link:0 "一股强大的灵能反噬从灵能界的连接中弹出来，进入了所有 [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] 共享的灵能连接中。"
ADD curse.ship.link:0 "A powerful psychic backlash has bounced back through our conduit with the Shroud, and it seems to be affecting our ships."
CN2 curse.ship.link:0 "一股强大的灵能反噬从灵能界的连接中弹出来，对我们的所有飞船造成了影响。"
ADD utopia.3050.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nThis has had a profound effect on the happiness of our citizens, and a sense of gloom now pervades throughout the [Root.GetName]. Even the mundanes can feel it."
CN2 utopia.3050.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$该事件对我们公民的幸福造成了严重的影响，忧郁的感觉充斥在 [Root.GetName] 之中。就连普通人也可以清楚地感应到。"
ADD utopia.3051.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nThis negative energy has spread doubt within the minds of our citizens. Many are turning towards new radical ideas that are not in line with those of our government. The effect has even spread to non-psychic citizens!"
CN2 utopia.3051.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$一种负能源快速散播在我们公民的心中。他们其中的许多人开始提出反对我们政府的激进观念。此状态甚至传播到了非灵能者公民中！"
ADD utopia.3052.desc:0 "$curse.ship.link$\n\nTheir armor has grown brittle, and can no longer sustain the punishment it once could."
CN2 utopia.3052.desc:0 "$curse.ship.link$他们的装甲变得比以往更易破碎，导致他们无法像以往一样承受那么多的攻击。"
ADD utopia.3053.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nFor some reason, this has had a detrimental effect on birth-rates throughout the [Root.GetName]. This has even affected members of races without any inherent psionic ability!"
CN2 utopia.3053.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$不知何因， [Root.GetName] 的出生率受到了不利的影响。这一效果甚至影响到了没有灵能能力的种族！"
ADD utopia.3054.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nThe minds of our researchers have been clouded, and they are having great difficulty focusing on their work."
CN2 utopia.3054.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$我们的研究员的思想变得模糊不清，难以集中精力去工作。"
ADD utopia.3055.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nThe rate at which we accumulate political influence has been greatly diminished."
CN2 utopia.3055.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$我们累积政治影响力的速度被显著削弱了。"
ADD utopia.3056.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nThe sense of unity that once existed between our citizens has been shattered."
CN2 utopia.3056.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$我们人民曾经团结一致的精神被彻底粉碎了。"
ADD utopia.3057.desc:0 "$curse.ship.link$\n\nOur ships move as if some kind of invisible force is holding them back, like a rubber-band. This has resulted in much slower sub-light travel."
CN2 utopia.3057.desc:0 "$curse.ship.link$我们的飞船就像被一种无形的力量所牵制着一般，亚光速航行的速度被显著减慢。"
ADD utopia.3058.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$\n\nThis negative energy has eroded the morale of our ground troops, who will be much less effective in battle for a time."
CN2 utopia.3058.desc:0 "$curse.psi.link$该负能源侵蚀了我们地面部队的士气，导致他们的战斗力暂时性降低。"
ADD utopia.3059.desc:0 "A powerful psychic backlash has bounced back through our conduit with the Shroud, and it seems to be interfering with our interstellar sensors.\n\nThe sensor resolution from all sources has been greatly diminished, resulting in much shorter sensor ranges."
CN2 utopia.3059.desc:0 "一股强大的灵能反噬从灵能界的连接中弹出来，开始干扰着我们的星际传感器。\n\n我们布置于宇宙各地的传感器的解析度出现显著的降低，导致我们的探测范围急剧缩小。"
