ADD utopia.3100.desc:0 "[Root.Capital.GetName]... the vision is hazy and indistinct, but there can be no question - it is [Root.Capital.GetName], our capital. The great cities look different yet familiar, even through the obscuring wall of flames and smoke. Thousands... no, millions of mutilated bodies litter the streets, all of them [Root.GetSpeciesName]. The stench of decay is unbearable.\n\n§P"YOUR FUTURE."§!\n\nNothing living remains in the ruins. In the sky above, massive orbital installations, trailing smoke, have begun a slow and inevitable descent towards the planet. Are we witnessing one possible future out of many?\n\n§P"NOT ONE OF MANY. IT SHALL COME TO PASS. AS SURELY AS THE SUN RISES. IT IS YOUR DESTINY."§!\n\nThe vision ends as quickly as it began, leaving behind a miasma of swirling psychic energies."
CN2 utopia.3100.desc:0 " [Root.Capital.GetName] ……幻象虽然模糊不清，但很明显——那是我们的首都 [Root.Capital.GetName] 。入眼所见的一个个熟悉的城市此时显得有点陌生，而且到处都是一道道冲天而起的火焰和浓烟。数以百万的残缺尸体散落在街道上，全部都是 [Root.GetSpeciesName] 。一道道腐烂的恶臭味扑鼻而来。\n\n§P"此乃汝之未来。"§!\n\n废墟中毫无生命的迹象。天空之上，大量的轨道站带着浓浓的尾烟朝着地面直冲而下。我们这是在目击着无数种未来的其中一个吗？\n\n§P"此非其一也。此乃实。犹如日出。此乃汝之命运。"§!\n\n幻觉来得快，去也快，只留下一团灵能在空气中缓缓消散。"
