ADD utopia.3110.desc:0 "This is a particularly tempestuous region of the Shroud. Massive currents of raw psionic energy is funneled through here, sometimes giving violent birth to semi-intelligent spiritual apparitions.\n\nThese confused spirits often clash with one another, unleashing massive amounts of psychic power in battles that can last millennia. In fact, several such duels seem to be taking place right now.\n\nWe should proceed with caution."
CN2 utopia.3110.desc:0 "这里是灵能界中最暴乱的区域。大量的原始灵能流排入此处，偶尔甚至会诞生出半智力精神力生物。这些混乱的灵魂会经常发生冲突，并在战斗中释放大量的可以遗留千年的灵能能力。而现在恰恰就有数场混战正在发生。我们必须谨慎行事。"
ADD utopia.3120.desc:0 "In the deeper regions of the Shroud, a presence suddenly makes itself felt. Visitors, like us - a powerful psionic probe made by minds as utterly alien to us as they are to the Shroud.\n\nA faint image of massive organic beings floating in some kind of thick, gaseous atmosphere while being attended by swarms of smaller creatures flickers briefly into existence as their psychic echo touches our own."
CN2 utopia.3120.desc:0 "在灵能界的深处，某个存在突然现身。正如我们一样，对方也是拜访此地的外来者——这个由灵能所制造的强大外星人探测器跟我们一样对灵能界非常陌生。对方的心灵波动跟我们接触时，我们在那一瞬间看见了一些模糊的影像：一个个巨大的有机生物漂浮在浓厚气体的大气层中，而它们周围则围绕着一群群较小型的生物。"
ADD utopia.3130.desc:0 "An endless desert stretches before us. We have been here before.\n\n§P"Shala'kul milem zunak?"§!\n\nSomething emerges from the sand. It is difficult to see.\n\n§P"Zharabi, melasuk."§!\n\nThe words are like thunder, spoken by a mouth for which they were never intended. We are compelled to answer."
CN2 utopia.3130.desc:0 "入眼所见是一片无边无际的沙漠。我们曾经到过这里。\n\n§P"Shala'kul milem zunak？"§!有什么东西在沙子中浮现出来，但是画面模糊不清。§P"Zharabi，melasuk。"§!对方的话语犹如打雷般响彻云霄。我们无法不回答。"
ADD utopia.3130.a:0 "Shashka malak."
CN2 utopia.3130.a:0 "Shashka malak。"
ADD utopia.3130.b:0 "Tirit nali dasumara!"
CN2 utopia.3130.b:0 "Tirit nali dasumara！"
ADD utopia.3130.c:0 "Kunak de'Kirak."
CN2 utopia.3130.c:0 "Kunak de'Kirak。"
ADD utopia.3140.desc:0 "Suddenly, in a painful moment of clarity, the nature of our existence is laid bare. A multiverse where thousands of galaxies like our own are locked in endless cycles of conflict.\n\nIt begins, it ends, and then it begins again. Each time with trillions of lives hanging in the balance.\n\n§P"So it is,"§! a voice whispers, §P"and so it shall always be."§!"
CN2 utopia.3140.desc:0 "一瞬间，我们清晰地看见了我们存在的本质。成千上万个跟我们一样的星系被锁在无穷无尽的冲突中。开始、结束、周而复始。每一次都有数以千万亿的生命危在旦夕。§P"就是如此"§!一个声音低声道，§P"永远都该如此。"§!"
ADD utopia.3150.desc:0 "We are looking down upon our galaxy from far above, at a distance of what must be hundreds of thousands of lightyears. Without warning, the psionic current plunges us down towards the myriad stars at an incredible speed, into the region of space belonging to one of the Fallen Empires - the [fallen_empire.GetName].\n\nStars swish by, then planets, until the vision finally settled on a [fallen_empire.GetSpeciesName] city. Incredible spires rise towards the sky, aided by anti-grav technology generations beyond our own. The current takes us into such a spire, through wall after wall until we reach a large meeting room of sorts. It is occupied by two [fallen_empire.GetSpeciesNamePlural], floating comfortably in zero-gravity chairs while conversing with each other in soft voices.\n\nThey are oblivious to our presence."
CN2 utopia.3150.desc:0 "我们正在从很高处俯视我们的宇宙，大概是有上千光年的距离吧。这时候突然有一股灵能流毫无预警地将我们冲下到某个失落帝国—— [fallen_empire.GetName] 的领土中。 \n\n在无数天体和星球中嗖嗖的穿行，我们的视野最终停留在 [fallen_empire.GetSpeciesName] 的某个城市中。映入眼帘的是一个个使用远超我们科技的反重力技术所支撑起来的直冲云霄的螺旋状建筑。这股灵流将我们带到其中一个建筑上，穿过一层又一层的墙壁直至我们到达了一个类似于会议室的巨大房间中。房间中有两个 [fallen_empire.GetSpeciesNamePlural] ，他们坐在舒适的反重力椅子上轻声地聊天。对方似乎完全没察觉到我们的存在。"
ADD utopia.3150.a:0 "§YReach into their minds in search of secrets.§!"
CN2 utopia.3150.a:0 "§Y进入他们的脑海搜寻秘密。§!"
