ADD utopia.3400.desc:0 "The immortal entity known as §H[chosen_one.GetName]§!, previously [chosen_one_species.GetName] but now something far more, has attracted a large and devout following in the [Root.GetName]. Worshipped by many as a supreme deity, a call has gone out to officially crown the [chosen_one.GetTitle] as the permanent ruler of our great empire, now and into perpetuity."
CN2 utopia.3400.desc:0 "一个名为§H [chosen_one.GetName] §!的人拥有不死之身，之前是一个 [chosen_one_species.GetName] ，现在已经远远超出了那个范畴，他在 [Root.GetName] 吸引了大量虔诚的信徒。很多人都把他当做神，据说已经正式被授予了 [chosen_one.GetTitle] 的称号，并成为了我们伟大帝国永远的统治者，从现在直到永远。"
ADD utopia.3400.a:0 "A powerful psychic, but a God? Hardly."
CN2 utopia.3400.a:0 "是个强大的灵能者，但是说是神？这就不太可信了。"
ADD utopia.3400.b:0 "May [chosen_one.GetHerHis] reign stretch into infinity... and beyond!"
