ADD utopia.3401.desc:0 "An immensely powerful [chosen_one_species.GetName] psychic has seized control of the §H[From.GetName]§!! This immortal being, referred to in hushed whispers as the "Chosen One" by [chosen_one.GetHerHis] followers, was crowned on [From.Capital.GetName] in a lavish ceremony this morning. A communique celebrating the eternal rule of §H[chosen_one.GetRulerTitle] [chosen_one.GetRegnalName]§! was sent out to all interstellar governments shortly thereafter."
CN2 utopia.3401.desc:0 "一个十分强大的 [chosen_one_species.GetName] 灵能者控制了§H [From.GetName] §!!这个不死之人被 [chosen_one.GetHerHis] 的追随者称为"天选之子"，今天早上在 [From.Capital.GetName] 隆重的典礼中加冕。这是§H [chosen_one.GetRulerTitle] 永久统治的宣告。 [chosen_one.GetRegnalName] §!稍后就被派往了其他星际行政系统。"
ADD utopia.3401.a:0 "[chosen_one.GetName] has been touched by the Shroud."
